Revision history for Perl extension App-GAWM

{{$NEXT}}
    - MongoDB 4.0.1
    - MongoDB Perl Driver 2.0.1
    - Perl 5.18
    - Skip tests if MongoDB not installed
    - Use estimated_document_count to replace deprecated count()
    - Add `bson_codec    => BSON->new( prefer_numeric => 1, ),` to MongoDB::MongoClient->new()
    - No longer need OID

0.0.6 2017-10-10T09:02:54Z
    - Use the 'count' method from MongoDB::Collection

0.0.5 2017-01-14T18:44:36Z
    - -f for --file
    - Stopwatch for init

0.0.4 2017-01-13T15:36:38Z
